This repository is a cleaned distribution extracted from a production deployment.

Base upstream:
- https://github.com/Wei-Shaw/claude-relay-service

What changed in this distribution:
- removed machine-specific deployment wrappers, VPN scripts, subscription files, logs, backups, and local domains
- kept the runnable relay service, admin UI build artifacts, pricing data, and core maintenance scripts
- documented direct and proxy-based deployment paths for third-party operators
